      "role": "user",
      "content": "we already checked the logs and the counting staff seems solid. everything is being scanned in and out correctly, it's just like... they're just gone. nothing's showing as \"damaged\" or \"returned,\" just missing from the shelf.\n\nthe variance is always negative, never positive. do you have any other theories on why items would just vanish in small batches like this without leaving a trail in the system?",
