      "content": "we checked the staging area too. cameras are fine and nothing unusual is happening during transitions. it's just these weird, tiny amounts of hardware just disappearing. \n\nit's almost like they're being taken by something that isn't even trying to hide, just small enough to be ignored. is there any technical or environmental reason why a component might just \"disappear\" from a tally without a paper trail?",
